WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.120
Now, quick story behind this.

00:00:02.120 --> 00:00:04.720
I call him, his name is Keith, but I call him Grandad

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:06.560
because he always said to me,

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:08.280
I'm the grand sonny never lad.

00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:10.880
So we kind of always drink together, we talk together.

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:13.760
So between Chris from the rugby and Grandad,

00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:14.840
if you like, from the bros,

00:00:14.840 --> 00:00:18.440
if I don't bring either of them for one day,

00:00:18.440 --> 00:00:19.520
they think there's something wrong

00:00:19.520 --> 00:00:21.600
or I'm in hospital or something,

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:23.440
I'm away for some reason.

00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:25.360
So I talk to them every day.

00:00:25.360 --> 00:00:26.200
Both of them?

00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:27.040
Yeah.

00:00:27.040 --> 00:00:28.080
So they're your two best friends.

00:00:28.080 --> 00:00:28.920
Yeah, definitely.

00:00:28.920 --> 00:00:32.040
A oes gennych chi ffrindiau o'ch leiaf?

00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:33.480
Ie, felly mae gen i John,

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:35.120
sydd fy mhwyl yn y ffyrdd,

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:37.280
a byddwn i'n meddwl gyda'i hefyd.

00:00:37.280 --> 00:00:38.800
Nid ydym yn gweithio'n bach ar ddi,

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:41.720
ond rydym yn ymwneud â phan o ddau o blynyddoedd

00:00:41.720 --> 00:00:42.560
mewn i'n meddwl.

00:00:42.560 --> 00:00:44.360
Felly dyna ydym yn dweud,

00:00:44.360 --> 00:00:45.520
oherwydd Chris ydym yn ymwneud â phan o ddi

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:46.880
a Keith ydym yn ymwneud â phan o ddi.

00:00:46.880 --> 00:00:48.560
Felly dyna pam rydw i'n gweithio â'i ddau.

00:00:48.560 --> 00:00:52.080
Felly, John, rydym yn ymwneud â phan o ddi.

00:00:52.080 --> 00:00:54.120
John, rydw i'n ymwneud â'i ddau o bryd,

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:56.280
oherwydd ein tais o ffyrdd.

00:00:56.280 --> 00:00:57.560
Oherwydd rydw i'n ddod yn oed yn cwyl,

00:00:57.560 --> 00:00:58.840
ac oherwydd bod hi'n bwysig â John,

00:00:58.840 --> 00:01:01.400
rydw i wedi cael ei ddod i ddod i ffyrdd môl

00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:02.400
fel ymlaen,

00:01:02.400 --> 00:01:03.600
fel Justin Timberlake,

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:05.080
Mae Bwm 5 a beth sydd.

00:01:06.520 --> 00:01:08.040
Ond rydw i wedi cael ei ddod i ddod i ffyrdd,

00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:09.640
fel y ffyrdd o'r 50s, o'r 60s,

00:01:09.640 --> 00:01:10.720
o'r 70s.

00:01:10.720 --> 00:01:12.520
Felly rydw i fel,

00:01:12.520 --> 00:01:14.520
Felly, ffyrdd,

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:17.080
